{"tid":1276511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個廢青對於有人話琴日沖擊係破壞法治嘅睇法","createTime":"2019-07-02T03:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:11:45.000Z","uid":151116,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8581b028236276e63ba4c29163f7203d5ea5072e","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"法治本身有四個層次：<br />\n有法可依<br />\n有法必依<br />\n以法限權<br />\n以法達義<br />\n香港屬於邊個層次？我覺得最多係第二個 以法限權 收皮啦!香港啲「差佬」完全冇人管到612大家睇到喇! 個政府又係完全冇反應嘅冇人限制到佢嘅!<br />\n<br />\n 老實講今次擺到明就係個局，但點解啲年青人會選擇衝入去，甚至有啲係已經寫好曬遺書，因為佢哋真係感到好絕望!佢哋衝擊立法會我知道係犯法㗎但係我理解佢地喎。<br />\n<br />\n有啲人話嗰啲人係暴徒係鬼，雖然佢哋真係有錯但係已經死咗三個人啦，有咩畀人命更加重要呀， 呢個時間篤灰好咩？ 一百萬二百萬都出過嚟啦， 成個城市四分一人口都出咗嚟個垃圾政府有理過我哋咩？No 示威者係一個點嘅情況底下先畀人逼到佢衝，可唔可以請大家諗下。<br />\n<br />\n612都係示威者衝先得到個「暫緩」，但係垃圾會個議事規則係冇暫緩呢一回事，只有押後同埋撤回，簡單啲嚟講個垃圾政府你完全冇理過我哋水緊我哋咋!<br />\n<br />\n示威者真係破壞法治？ 錯呀!<br />\n我哋係爭取緊法治呀!<br />\n爭取緊嘅一個更加高層次嘅法治!"},{"pid":"f4b22d8c1ef4d28ec68522fef51c83f43af5e2f5","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e989fe152e32e3dc6d0196b8a1a4edd7f25979f","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77f41fda91f3030fb8ffca74687e340dbfae43a7","tid":1276511,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/64993?20190702&amp;fbclid=IwAR2_ZWGr6HA7Wxq8srUDp0V0vVzcYUfwkVKkwx4aqyL3yPgaWZrSuV4sXMs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F64993%3F20190702%26fbclid%3DIwAR2_ZWGr6HA7Wxq8srUDp0V0vVzcYUfwkVKkwx4aqyL3yPgaWZrSuV4sXMs&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=cb76aaed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/64993?20190702&amp;fbclid=IwAR2_ZWGr6HA7Wxq8srUDp0V0vVzcYUfwkVKkwx4aqyL3yPgaWZrSuV4sXMs</a><br />\n<br />\n破壞法治的從來只有政府。<br />\n抗爭者破壞的極其量是法律，但爭取的是真正的法治"},{"pid":"0afcbab4df1e80875272ea250f23487d89428307","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"653abdcb8b98b8ee1fdbcc64f27fcc63a4be5e16","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df88bf57d95ca0c6d7105745305305802285b417","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1de812b41243daa9be5b82106d340ea0cac77c27","tid":1276511,"uid":151116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"法治指以民意授權為前提和基礎立法，以嚴格依法管治國家為核心，以制約權力為關鍵的社會管理機制、社會活動方式和社會秩序狀態。法治的內涵，不單是要求所有人民守法，更側重於法律對政府權力的控制和拘束。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=89d22738\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB</a>"}]}